Pointer Offshore III, Ltd.  Financing
Pointer Offshore III, Ltd. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite equity financing.  Pointer Offshore III, Ltd. was able to sell $342,640,565. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 26 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $5,000,000. The financing document was filed on 2015-10-09. Pointer Offshore III, Ltd. is based in  735 BROAD STREET, SUITE 1108  CHATTANOOGA 37402. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Joseph Davenport III.





